<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I use a ZendMVC Application to write text based config files for a nagios system.
A view script is used as a template and filled with values from the controller side.
If the last character on a line is a closing php tag ?&gt; the following new line gets lost in the rendered output.</p>

<p>Example:
Keyword: &lt;?= $sKeydata ?&gt;
Keyword: &lt;?= $sKeydata ?&gt;</p>

<p>Becomes:</p>

<p>Keyword: KeydataKeyword: Keydata</p>

    </div>
</div>

