        <div class="body">
            <p>This is a limitation of PHP, and how it handles newlines following a closing "?&gt;" tag. There are two workarounds:</p>

<ul><li>add whitespace following the closing tag prior to the newline</li>
<li>add an extra newline</li>
</ul>
        </div>
    </div>
